##Notes for Week 5: 2.1 Demonstration: The Production of Tennis Balls

Based on an in class demonstration the intuitive suggestion for the [production function][], [marginal product][] and [diminishing marginal product] are presented.

The increase of number of workers in the production line for tennis balls illustrates very well the effect that this has in the [diminishing marginal product] for _"producing"_ tennis balls.

[production function]: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Production_function
[marginal product]: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marginal_product
[diminishing marginal product]: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diminishing_returns
